snippet.title: Plants vs Zombies Battle for Neighborville Deluxe Edition Upgrade!
snippet.description:
If you buy an Origin Access Premier subscription for at least one month, then you will automatically upgrade your game to Deluxe Editions and get all these bonuses, plus bonuses for an EA subscription. You can find out about them here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PfNsSoBQ5i4

DELUX EDITION Plants vs Zombies Battle for Neighborville
